    "As the notion of \"sufficiency\" is not legally defined and until specific standards or guidelines elaborate on the matter, it is at the discretion of AI providers to weight up their datasets against the \"sufficiency\" scale, considering the application and the context at hand.",
    "A level of legal uncertainty arises in that regard.",
